data.description: Spacious 4BR, 2BA brick home with an inviting outdoor pool. This property offers the perfect canvas for customization with some cosmetic updates. Featuring a generous 1946 sqft of living space, it's ideal for a family home or investment opportunity. The property also includes a convenient shed for storage. Located in a great neighborhood, this home has excellent potential.
